name: PocketNanoCells
description:
PocketNanoCells - spread the vaccine with nanobots in infected cells PocketNanoCells is a game in which you have to find and treat infected cells with the help of nanobots! Get resources for distributing the vaccine. Upgrade your nano rockets.

PocketNanoCells  is currently being developed solo game developer. To get the latest updates be sure to follow me on Insagram.  Thanks for checking out our game and we can't wait to share all the exciting updates we have planned for it!
